OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation into the
OL,7,Fpotential dangers of travelling abroad
OL,8,Ffor cosmetic surgery has revealed the
OL,9,Flack of aftercare is one of the
OL,10,Fbiggest risks.
OL,12,FSome patients find themselves being
OL,13,Fdischarged from clinics, despite
OL,14,Fsuffering from complications.
OL,16,FThose who return to the UK with
OL,17,Fserious health problems may struggle
OL,18,Fto find the care they need, without
OL,19,Fhefty financial consequences.
