OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,FSo, what are your rights and where can
OL,7,Fyou turn?
OL,9,FWho is responsible for my aftercare
OL,10,Fafter cosmetic surgery abroad ?
OL,12,FThe NHS policy is very clear: if you
OL,13,Fhave complications after cosmetic
OL,14,Fsurgery, it is the surgeon's
OL,15,Fresponsibility to provide follow-up
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,FHowever, overseas clinics may not
OL,19,Fprovide aftercare or may not provide
OL,20,Fit to the same standard as in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
