OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,FAlso, they may not have a healthcare
OL,7,Fprofessional in the UK to help you if
OL,8,Fyou have any problems once you get
OL,9,Fback.
OL,11,FIf something goes wrong overseas, will
OL,12,Fthe British Embassy help ?
OL,14,FThe Foreign Office website says: "The
OL,15,FFCDO cannot usually help if you have
OL,16,Ftravelled abroad for medical
OL,17,Ftreatment, for example if you have
OL,18,Fissues with the care received or costs
OL,19,Finvolved.
