OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,F"Planned medical treatment is
OL,7,Fconsidered a commercial arrangement."
OL,9,FCan I turn to the NHS once I am home?
OL,11,FThe British Association of Plastic
OL,12,FReconstructive and Aesthetic Surgeons
OL,13,F(BAPRAS) is blunt about this, it says:
OL,14,F"If you have a problem following
OL,15,Fsurgery then the people who carried
OL,16,Fout should be there to help you
OL,17,Fresolve it: the NHS is not there to
OL,18,Funderwrite cut-price surgery abroad."
