OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,FIt says NHS Trusts and commissioners
OL,7,Fwill usually refuse treatment for less
OL,8,Fserious complications or bad outcomes
OL,9,Ffollowing cosmetic surgery in the UK
OL,10,For abroad.
OL,12,FHowever, the NHS will look after
OL,13,Fanyone who is facing a life-
OL,14,Fthreatening emergency.
