OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,FAnd BAPRAS says it has noticed an
OL,7,Fincreasing number of patients turning
OL,8,Fto the NHS with problems following
OL,9,Fcosmetic surgery abroad. It estimates
OL,10,Fthe average cost to the NHS to treat
OL,11,Fthose with complications from surgery
OL,12,Fabroad is #15,000 per patient.
OL,14,FIf you want to share your experience
OL,15,Fof cosmetic surgery or procedures with
OL,16,FITV News, you can contact our
OL,17,Finvestigations team at
OL,18,Finvestigations@itv.com
