OL,3,CCosmetic surgery abroad - What are
OL,4,Cyour aftercare rights?
OL,6,FPolicies vary, but in general it is
OL,7,Funusual for a holiday policy to cover
OL,8,Fyou in the event of something going
OL,9,Fwrong during or after planned surgery
OL,10,Foutside the UK.
OL,12,FThe Association of British Insurers
OL,13,Fsays there are exclusions in most
OL,14,Finsurance policies for any kind of
OL,15,Felective surgery.
OL,17,FHowever, specialist insurance is
OL,18,Favailable for such trips. You may also
OL,19,Fbe covered by the clinic or surgeon's
OL,20,Finsurance policy.
